OL,3,CMiddlesbrough FC call for Southampton
OL,4,Cto be kicked out of Championship play-
OL,5,Coffs
OL,7,FMiddlesbrough have called for
OL,8,FSouthampton to be kicked out of the
OL,9,FChampionship play-offs over spying
OL,10,Fallegations.
OL,12,FThe Saints were charged by the EFL
OL,13,Flast Friday following accusations a
OL,14,Ftraining session at Middlesbrough's
OL,15,FRockliffe Park complex was observed
OL,16,Ftwo days before the sides met in a
OL,17,Fplay-off semi-final first leg.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
