FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779012401
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough FC call for Southampton
OL,4,Cto be kicked out of Championship play-
OL,5,Coffs
OL,7,FMiddlesbrough confirmed on Friday they
OL,8,Fhad sought to be a party in the
OL,9,Findependent commission hearing but
OL,10,Fwere denied the opportunity.
OL,12,F"The club regrets that outcome, given
OL,13,Fwe are directly affected by the
OL,14,Fmatters under consideration and hold
OL,15,Frelevant factual evidence as to the
OL,16,Fevents in question and their
OL,17,Fcompetitive impact," a statement from
OL,18,Fthe club read.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779012401
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough FC call for Southampton
OL,4,Cto be kicked out of Championship play-
OL,5,Coffs
OL,7,F"The conduct at issue, namely the
OL,8,Fobservation and recording of our
OL,9,Ftraining session ahead of a fixture of
OL,10,Fsuch significance, goes to the heart
OL,11,Fof sporting integrity and fair
OL,12,Fcompetition.
OL,14,F"In these circumstances, the only
OL,15,Fappropriate response is a sporting
OL,16,Fsanction which would prevent
OL,17,FSouthampton FC from participating in
OL,18,Fthe EFL Championship play-off final."
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
