FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779012401
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough FC call for Southampton
OL,4,Cto be kicked out of Championship play-
OL,5,Coffs
OL,7,FBoro urged the EFL to pursue a
OL,8,Fsporting sanction against Southampton
OL,9,Fat the hearing "in order to protect
OL,10,Fthe integrity of the game, safeguard
OL,11,Fall member clubs, and deter any
OL,12,Fattempt in the future to obtain an
OL,13,Funfair and unlawful advantage in
OL,14,Fpursuit of promotion to the Premier
OL,15,FLeague".
OL,17,FThe statement concluded: "The club
OL,18,Freserves all its legal rights."
OL,26,@qD@POUwD@GO]yD@ZOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
