PN,42405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779012401
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough FC call for Southampton
OL,4,Cto be kicked out of Championship play-
OL,5,Coffs
OL,7,FIt is understood Boro have enlisted
OL,8,Fthe services of top sports lawyer Nick
OL,9,FDe Marco in this case.
OL,11,FThe 'Spygate' proceedings could force
OL,12,Fa delay to the play-off final on 23
OL,13,FMay.
OL,15,FThe initial hearing will take place on
OL,16,For before next Tuesday, but an appeal
OL,17,Fmay also need to be heard before next
OL,18,FSaturday, creating a week of
OL,19,Funcertainty for fans, players and
OL,20,Fstaff of Southampton, their final
OL,21,Fopponents Hull and Middlesbrough.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
