PN,42406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1779012401
OL,3,CMiddlesbrough FC call for Southampton
OL,4,Cto be kicked out of Championship play-
OL,5,Coffs
OL,7,FThe EFL said on Thursday it had "a
OL,8,Fnumber of contingency plans" in place
OL,9,Fdepending on the outcome of the legal
OL,10,Fproceedings. Tickets went on sale to
OL,11,FSouthampton and Hull fans on Friday
OL,12,Fmorning.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
